{"tid":857891,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[係咪我嘅問題] 唔知幾時開始覺得香港好恐怖","createTime":"2018-10-11T11:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T00:52:26.000Z","uid":125976,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0413fbd2a83b77fa8d250861225a4eed15ed2499","tid":857891,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"人口密度愈嚟愈高，撘車又逼食飯又逼，而家連出街都唔想出。<br />\n<br />\n國際排名愈來愈低，各方面都睇得出香港嘅守舊同落後 (eg. IT、法律、金融)<br />\n<br />\n文化上愈來愈接近支那，當權者濫用權力收窄公民應有嘅人權同自由，但啲人開始好奇怪咁合理化佢嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n人口大增，但經濟結構守舊單一，令到人均生產力增長慢，但社會開支又大。再加上政府亂洗錢同官商勾結，導致資源 (eg. 醫療、教育) 唔夠分，遲早過過跟支那一齊食草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2d0980030abc73fb214bab399ff184105e6b47","tid":857891,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"溫水煮蛙<br />\n慢慢加熱令人感覺唔到變化<br />\n但同十年前對比已經知道大陸對香港控制愈來愈大"},{"pid":"99422a13efb45b323e5139f1623b7faff33c566b","tid":857891,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e2d0980030abc73fb214bab399ff184105e6b47","tid":857891,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"溫水煮蛙<br />\n慢慢加熱令人感覺唔到變化<br />\n但同十年前對比已經知道大陸對香港控制愈來愈大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"慢性勞改，支那思想注入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb40808b088812f36649ff4190356bdbebd197e","tid":857891,"uid":66866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6aa79ac421933c4d3145fd5c16fedece83258f","tid":857891,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:03:22.000Z","msg":"港共政府好識利用社會嘅痛處去收服人民嘅心，令大眾信服投靠中共係唯一選擇，長期麻醉之下好多人逐漸成為順民"},{"pid":"72faabbb42f7c5deb830ab1709b03235a17c781d","tid":857891,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e2d0980030abc73fb214bab399ff184105e6b47","tid":857891,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"溫水煮蛙<br />\n慢慢加熱令人感覺唔到變化<br />\n但同十年前對比已經知道大陸對香港控制愈來愈大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"而家都接近滾水"},{"pid":"fb27d9a138dee98f8b0e3c96ed149c4f3618cad5","tid":857891,"uid":60297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:30:13.000Z","msg":"被一個無質素嘅國家管治<br />\n合附預期啦"},{"pid":"67681fea54d3db3accc794c7736573e2ac3c4434","tid":857891,"uid":136061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"道出左重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  駁唔到"},{"pid":"5d5e5afb432321d196c309f84b2bd58a7137903b","tid":857891,"uid":90457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"俾樹砸死---&gt;跳樓自殺，咁樣睇其實好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但諗深一層，呢個係香港第一單「被自殺」"},{"pid":"dbd271d4d66073ea8ee9253acc1823df7684634f","tid":857891,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"歷史黎，強國中意慢慢過d支那人去消滅當地文化同時令自己文化紮根"},{"pid":"a805716c1e23832f1f032425a457e3c696f92c80","tid":857891,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"cd35086b03540ae30d98cfaf11a395dfcb4775ba","tid":857891,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a805716c1e23832f1f032425a457e3c696f92c80","tid":857891,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70286fb4a2d3b6e82952644b01f6784040a14d9","tid":857891,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd35086b03540ae30d98cfaf11a395dfcb4775ba","tid":857891,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a805716c1e23832f1f032425a457e3c696f92c8