img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近發現啲港豬黐晒線，個個都好似想殺人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}